    "format": "(UINT32) Status",
    "remarks_html": "<p>Contains the result of a game list status update.</p>\n<p>Possible values for Status:</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Status</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x00</code></td>\n<td>Ok</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x01</code></td>\n<td><em>A game by that name already exists!</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x02</code></td>\n<td><em>Unable to create game because the selected game type is currently unavailable.</em></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>0x03</code></td>\n<td><em>An error occurred while trying to create the game.</em></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
    "comments": [
